<div class="sh-hero">
  <div>
    <h1>Custom Python <span class="sh-accent">Trading Platform</span></h1>
    <p>
      A quantitative trading platform for Nasdaq-100 futures built on tick-level order-flow analysis — volume
      profile, anchored VWAP, range bars and a six-method absorption detector, with Gaussian-HMM regime
      classification. It backtests through a Streamlit research framework and Monte Carlo prop-firm simulators,
      then runs live: four concurrent strategies, coordinated under a no-hedge rule, executing across NinjaTrader 8
      and MetaTrader 5 with heartbeat failsafes and per-account risk management.
    </p>
    <div class="sh-tech">
      <span>Python</span><span>Databento</span><span>pandas · NumPy · Polars</span>
      <span>scikit-learn · hmmlearn</span><span>Streamlit · Plotly</span>
      <span>NinjaTrader 8 · C#</span><span>MetaTrader 5</span>
    </div>
  </div>
